                <note rend="inline" type="source">714.1515/763: Telegram</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The Minister in Duatemala</hi> (<persName type="from">
                        <hi rend="italic">Geissler</hi>
                    </persName>) <hi rend="italic">to the <gloss type="to">Secretary of
                            State</gloss>
                    </hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Guatemala</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1928-07-17T18:00:00-06:00">
                            <hi rend="italic">July 17, 1928—6 p.m.</hi>
                        </date>
                        <lb/>[Received July 18—12:10 a.m.]</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>95. The Legislative Assembly has passed the bill authorizing the Executive to
                    submit the boundary question to the International Central American Tribunal
                    without discussion and by unanimous vote. Repeated to Honduras.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Geissler</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
